                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-818-18450407 t18450407-818-punishment-16"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Coleridge.</hi>
